## Typography & spacing

### Text hierarchy

| Element | Style |
|---------|-------|
| Page title | `text-xl font-semibold` |
| Section header (large) | `text-lg font-semibold` |
| **Numbered chapter title** | `h3` + `text-sm font-semibold text-foreground` (sentence case) |
| **Subhead inside a chapter** | `text-xs font-medium text-foreground` |
| Subsection header (legacy / compact) | `text-xs font-semibold text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wide` |
| Labels | `text-sm text-muted-foreground` |
| Helper text | `text-xs text-muted-foreground` |

### Spacing scale

| Context | Value |
|---------|-------|
| Panel padding | `pt-6 space-y-6` |
| Section gap | `space-y-6` or `gap-6` |
| Chapter form (`divide-y`) | first section `pb-6`, middle `py-6`, actions `pt-6` |
| Component internal | `p-3`, `p-4` |
| Icon gaps | `gap-1`, `gap-2` |
| Inline spacing | `space-x-2`, `space-x-4` |

