## Icons (Lucide React)

Always use lucide-react icons. Common patterns:

```tsx
import {
  ChevronRight, // collapsed section
  ChevronDown, // expanded section
  ChevronUp, // collapse upward
  Trash2, // delete
  Edit2, // edit
  Plus, // add
  X, // close/cancel
  Check, // confirm
} from 'lucide-react'
```

